Experiment 8: Temperature Conversion (Celsius to Fahrenheit)
Aim
To write an algorithm for converting temperature from Celsius (°C) to Fahrenheit (°F).

Algorithm
1.Start
2.Declare variables: C (Celsius), F (Fahrenheit)
3.Input the temperature in Celsius (C)
4.Apply the conversion formula:
   F=(C×9/5)+32
5.Display the temperature in Fahrenheit (F)
6.Stop
